{"tid":1928650,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Microsoft公佈 Xbox series x完整性能 真機上手","createTime":"2020-03-16T13:33:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T18:38:56.000Z","uid":212473,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fffa995b1e45c28bddd42550a121263981417d2b","tid":1928650,"uid":212473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:33:03.000Z","msg":"微軟今日正式公開了Xbox Series X情報，Xbox Series X尺寸為151mm x 151mm x 301mm，<br />\n<br />\nXbox Series X上的《戰爭機器5》改進了接觸陰影以及光線追蹤屏幕空間全局光照明，所有的過場動畫在Xbox Series X上都能穩定60FPS以上運行，而在Xbox One X上只有30FPS。<br />\n<br />\n此外，在短短兩周內，《戰爭機器5》就完美移植到了Xbox Series X上，並且運行質量堪比PC上使用RTX 2080進行遊玩，和《賽博朋克2077》壹樣，已經擁有這款遊戲的玩家可以免費在Xbox Series X上遊玩。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2020/3/16/21152487/microsoft-xbox-series-x-specs-features-storage-cards-load-times-ray-tracing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2020%2F3%2F16%2F21152487%2Fmicrosoft-xbox-series-x-specs-features-storage-cards-load-times-ray-tracing&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebQAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=3c293d05\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theverge.com/2020/3/16/21152487/microsoft-xbox-series-x-specs-features-storage-cards-load-times-ray-tracing</a>"},{"pid":"1fc964552bf95eeb8c23a2a91cb24bc9742a1565","tid":1928650,"uid":212473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:43:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G8dRi-alZxc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DG8dRi-alZxc&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebQAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=5e196c65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G8dRi-alZxc</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QsFwKlMdF9s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQsFwKlMdF9s&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebQAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=f3442acf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QsFwKlMdF9s</a>"},{"pid":